              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2860 - رَوَى حَنَانُ بْنُ سَدِيرٍ قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:82:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/82/1",
        "text": [
          " : ذَكَرْتُ لِأَبِي جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ اَلْبَيْتَ فَقَالَ «لَوْ عَطَّلُوهُ سَنَةً وَاحِدَةً لَمْ يُنَاظَرُوا ».\nوَ فِي خَبَرٍ آخَرَ: «لَيَنْزِلُ عَلَيْهِمُ اَلْعَذَابُ »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2860 - Hanan ibn Sadir narrated: I mentioned the House (the Ka'bah) to Abu Ja'far (as),\nImam (as) said: \"If they were to abandon it for a single year, they would not be given respite.\"\nIn another narration, Imam (as) said: \"Punishment would descend upon them.\""
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
